{"tid":331934,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知sin 90點樣轉換做1","createTime":"2017-07-22T14:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T19:33:43.000Z","uid":80183,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b399bf66346e6cca5dcd5bbbfa4e130e1dde144e","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:42:14.000Z","msg":"E.g. Sin 90=1<br />\n我想知就咁俾sin 同90度<br />\nSin會係點樣將90度output做1<br />\nsin 呢個function係點樣既公式<br />\n由細到大都唔知sin係學緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e8c0e249e0b13308f64325ae7e45206e546bce","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:44:45.000Z","msg":"認真文都負評=.="},{"pid":"85f436e7d439db0028310e66469696eab8ed639b","tid":331934,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"應該係指緊sine wave 張圖"},{"pid":"1587d177b5343c408936ab1cb9f3fbdd4d40e706","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係指緊sine wave 張圖</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想問例如:有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換"},{"pid":"a531af321e70a94f834cecba4fb409208084a437","tid":331934,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"477d72f10181f8a122372b769d0f928e34e2136b","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>90蚊1q?</blockquote><br />\n認真文呀臭g=.="},{"pid":"950b4683607f1148783c69427be1e494a27278e0","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"求數學大神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edec59b8fb36f938abbd8dc6026cbbde94e05dc","tid":331934,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"淨係識taylor series 不過係約數"},{"pid":"df5381f21816c0e029a8c86de9e89c792c5c287b","tid":331934,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係指緊sine wave 張圖</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想問例如:有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png&h=7013c9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實去到大學就會學到Taylor Series<br />\n簡單黎講, 因為果條式不斷地approximate, 所以最後就會非常接近sin個function"},{"pid":"51d31246c976f75cd085cbdb8b8f3b037e4a3967","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係識taylor series 不過係約數</blockquote><br />\n可唔可講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝大神"},{"pid":"3eda4b9f38ce90066da9fc5133a4303379f0f9c4","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係指緊sine wave 張圖</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想問例如:有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png&h=7013c9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實去到大學就會學到Taylor Series<br />\n簡單黎講, 因為果條式不斷地approximate, 所以最後就會非常接近sin個function</blockquote><br />\n咁呢條式係其他sin情況岩唔岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEg.Sinh"},{"pid":"ac22cf9e2508b06c0fadd0d195b7eba918458f91","tid":331934,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係指緊sine wave 張圖</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想問例如:有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png&h=7013c9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實去到大學就會學到Taylor Series<br />\n簡單黎講, 因為果條式不斷地approximate, 所以最後就會非常接近sin個function</blockquote><br />\n咁呢條式係其他sin情況岩唔岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEg.Sinh</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.efunda.com/math/taylor_series/images/hyperbolic.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.efunda.com%2Fmath%2Ftaylor_series%2Fimages%2Fhyperbolic.gif&h=2a0ff1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據依張圖就應該係唔同既, 主要原因應該係d完個function之後係唔一樣答案, 不過我都已經唔係好記得sinh果D做咩"},{"pid":"4f4e77de7e08286917cd5672f08937b778b83e33","tid":331934,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:10:38.000Z","msg":"搭單問點解冇拍過拖要叫做a0<br />\n由細到大都係咁叫 但一直唔知原因<br />\n有冇大佬可以解答我"},{"pid":"d3aa46c34143ce0400287f7db257ad541bf97a38","tid":331934,"uid":76799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"Consider that<br />\n<br />\nr^2=x^2+y^2<br />\n<br />\nWhen theta = 90 degree <br />\n<br />\nx is 0<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, r^2=y^2<br />\n<br />\nr=y<br />\n<br />\nWe know that <br />\n<br />\nsin theta = y/r<br />\nsin 90 = r/r<br />\nsin 90 = 1<br />\n<br />\n再唔明，畫幅圖出黎就會明，數學唔可以死記，要理解，如有錯誤，歡迎指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a7510352fb511616f622b8565233554559531c","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係指緊sine wave 張圖</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想問例如:有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png&h=7013c9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實去到大學就會學到Taylor Series<br />\n簡單黎講, 因為果條式不斷地approximate, 所以最後就會非常接近sin個function</blockquote><br />\n咁呢條式係其他sin情況岩唔岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEg.Sinh</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.efunda.com/math/taylor_series/images/hyperbolic.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.efunda.com%2Fmath%2Ftaylor_series%2Fimages%2Fhyperbolic.gif&h=2a0ff1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據依張圖就應該係唔同既, 主要原因應該係d完個function之後係唔一樣答案, 不過我都已經唔係好記得sinh果D做咩</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打數學系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09861660f987c474cc16c33f07a3bbf719470ae2","tid":331934,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Consider that<br />\n<br />\nr^2=x^2+y^2<br />\n<br />\nWhen theta = 90 degree <br />\n<br />\nx is 0<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, r^2=y^2<br />\n<br />\nr=y<br />\n<br />\nWe know that <br />\n<br />\nsin theta = y/r<br />\nsin 90 = r/r<br />\nsin 90 = 1<br />\n<br />\n再唔明，畫幅圖出黎就會明，數學唔可以死記，要理解，如有錯誤，歡迎指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://mathworld.wolfram.com/images/eps-gif/Trigonometry_700.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmathworld.wolfram.com%2Fimages%2Feps-gif%2FTrigonometry_700.gif&h=e54be178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實用圓形幅圖都解釋到既, 因為如果90度, 係radius/radius = 1"},{"pid":"9deef6b593332396fb25e0b2f79e99beefd3b935","tid":331934,"uid":76799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係指緊sine wave 張圖</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想問例如:有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png&h=7013c9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實去到大學就會學到Taylor Series<br />\n簡單黎講, 因為果條式不斷地approximate, 所以最後就會非常接近sin個function</blockquote><br />\n唔需要用到大學數，中學數已夠"},{"pid":"36ab584151141f4015c2a942b39cf52bcb88d20f","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問點解冇拍過拖要叫做a0<br />\n由細到大都係咁叫 但一直唔知原因<br />\n有冇大佬可以解答我</blockquote><br />\n咪搞事臭g=.="},{"pid":"087af983876964df287516551ce2a121a1aacab8","tid":331934,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係指緊sine wave 張圖</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想問例如:有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png&h=7013c9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實去到大學就會學到Taylor Series<br />\n簡單黎講, 因為果條式不斷地approximate, 所以最後就會非常接近sin個function</blockquote><br />\n咁呢條式係其他sin情況岩唔岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEg.Sinh</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.efunda.com/math/taylor_series/images/hyperbolic.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.efunda.com%2Fmath%2Ftaylor_series%2Fimages%2Fhyperbolic.gif&h=2a0ff1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據依張圖就應該係唔同既, 主要原因應該係d完個function之後係唔一樣答案, 不過我都已經唔係好記得sinh果D做咩</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打數學系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟只係剛畢業既CS學生, 讀過一科1字頭既Math course而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2225882878b7f4ab7c4c5408ff436f17ca8a4e98","tid":331934,"uid":76799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"識prove sin 90 = 1 ，就會識prove cos 0 = 1"},{"pid":"f113b4169a36b5b80bda8b5beb966116e79b02ea","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係指緊sine wave 張圖</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想問例如:有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png&h=7013c9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實去到大學就會學到Taylor Series<br />\n簡單黎講, 因為果條式不斷地approximate, 所以最後就會非常接近sin個function</blockquote><br />\n唔需要用到大學數，中學數已夠</blockquote><br />\n多謝各位大大解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032117e4776f359d5b7f33d776bb531d13897137","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係指緊sine wave 張圖</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想問例如:有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F230024_aa0a5813a00772d0b81598cd6b5b38e6.png&h=7013c9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實去到大學就會學到Taylor Series<br />\n簡單黎講, 因為果條式不斷地approximate, 所以最後就會非常接近sin個function</blockquote><br />\n咁呢條式係其他sin情況岩唔岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEg.Sinh</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.efunda.com/math/taylor_series/images/hyperbolic.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.efunda.com%2Fmath%2Ftaylor_series%2Fimages%2Fhyperbolic.gif&h=2a0ff1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據依張圖就應該係唔同既, 主要原因應該係d完個function之後係唔一樣答案, 不過我都已經唔係好記得sinh果D做咩</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打數學系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟只係剛畢業既CS學生, 讀過一科1字頭既Math course而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCs都好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日要set algo"},{"pid":"3140eb7eeff92c670d54d504cbddbd3bed64d528","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識prove sin 90 = 1 ，就會識prove cos 0 = 1</blockquote><br />\n唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664bce2602ac0173af76ee573ef8607c7a712a54","tid":331934,"uid":76799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:20:48.000Z","msg":"學好d中學數啦，上到大學，你就會發現大學數好多都要中學數黎support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5719e3bae5bed633875a6b74616585070870a5a0","tid":331934,"uid":114946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"你係想問sine代表咩？<br />\n我會話係unit circle嘅投影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3b/Circle_cos_sin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F3b%2FCircle_cos_sin.gif&h=5cf69708&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9553787584a69fd4367f587ca290ea5c481e3935","tid":331934,"uid":54490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58b2a04f4805d38c187b66d2a713c24392baf00a","tid":331934,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:30:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bd6cdb7b05270786414338319f54cc7e7ca82d2","tid":331934,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:41:14.000Z","msg":"圓形圖最易get到。<br />\n呢個網好清楚<br />\n<a href=\"https://betterexplained.com/articles/intuitive-trigonometry/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbetterexplained.com%2Farticles%2Fintuitive-trigonometry%2F&d=HhOqQxtV6vaMmw0agYn3NNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=acb2be48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://betterexplained.com/articles/intuitive-trigonometry/</a>"},{"pid":"173492701e667719ef75ba61e2dbd6ec4558a0cd","tid":331934,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"a0做a1"},{"pid":"3e5d5157a0405f424bf414a9b5a50245dc6df1a9","tid":331934,"uid":117901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係想問sine代表咩？<br />\n我會話係unit circle嘅投影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3b/Circle_cos_sin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F3b%2FCircle_cos_sin.gif&h=5cf69708&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n正確答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554467dbc4dcc2fc311c44f68fabd7560514e192","tid":331934,"uid":128148,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"我會話係unit circle嘅投影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3b/Circle_cos_sin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F3b%2FCircle_cos_sin.gif&h=5cf69708&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]<br />\n用Taylor series係錯解，因為你要諗清楚証Taylor 的dy/dx已經係用左cos0=1,即sin90=0的定義。<br />\n<br />\n呢種解叫套套邏輯，用假設結論証明假設正確。<br />\n<br />\n樓上這位做的理解好好，值得欣賞。這條問題要答，就是因為「定義」！我地將三角函數引進廣義角時已講清楚：sin 角 = (unit circle的x坐標）咁自自然然sin90=1!<br />\n<br />\n勉強用番直角三角形解釋廣義角就不太恰當，因為自廣義角走出90度，正弦餘弦再不是邊比例，而是函數！"},{"pid":"d585a157bfab5d46861951c5db29ac2fd34e14e1","tid":331934,"uid":128148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會話係unit circle嘅投影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3b/Circle_cos_sin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F3b%2FCircle_cos_sin.gif&h=5cf69708&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n用Taylor series係錯解，因為你要諗清楚証Taylor 的dy/dx已經係用左cos0=1,即sin90=0的定義。<br />\n<br />\n呢種解叫套套邏輯，用假設結論証明假設正確。<br />\n<br />\n樓上這位做的理解好好，值得欣賞。這條問題要答，就是因為「定義」！我地將三角函數引進廣義角時已講清楚：sin 角 = (unit circle的x坐標）咁自自然然sin90=1!<br />\n<br />\n勉強用番直角三角形解釋廣義角就不太恰當，因為自廣義角走出90度，正弦餘弦再不是邊比例，而是函數！[/quote]<br />\n自膠先，打錯sin90=1"},{"pid":"d6a615508d46666c482d90222d33e2506f669952","tid":331934,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"sin function  = 一個直角三角形對邊除斜邊，即係兩條邊嘅比例<br />\n如果個直角三角形角度(x) 極細，~0, 咁對邊嘅長度都係0, 所以sin(x) = 0/i = 0, where i = any number &gt; 0<br />\n同時你又可以諗如果呢個三角形如果咁抵死係接近90度，只有對邊同斜邊長度好接近先可以做到，所以個比例=1<br />\n<br />\nbtw 其實前面有巴打貼出黎圓形投影嗰張圖好清楚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337220555c25b0e931ba5f862589e681b2a4ee9a","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我會話係unit circle嘅投影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3b/Circle_cos_sin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F3b%2FCircle_cos_sin.gif&h=5cf69708&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n用Taylor series係錯解，因為你要諗清楚証Taylor 的dy/dx已經係用左cos0=1,即sin90=0的定義。<br />\n<br />\n呢種解叫套套邏輯，用假設結論証明假設正確。<br />\n<br />\n樓上這位做的理解好好，值得欣賞。這條問題要答，就是因為「定義」！我地將三角函數引進廣義角時已講清楚：sin 角 = (unit circle的x坐標）咁自自然然sin90=1!<br />\n<br />\n勉強用番直角三角形解釋廣義角就不太恰當，因為自廣義角走出90度，正弦餘弦再不是邊比例，而是函數！</blockquote><br />\n自膠先，打錯sin90=1[/quote]<br />\n咁個sin wave function係咩公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad072ad8af94fbfdb82bfce68966db1b16e9ae5","tid":331934,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會話係unit circle嘅投影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3b/Circle_cos_sin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F3b%2FCircle_cos_sin.gif&h=5cf69708&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n用Taylor series係錯解，因為你要諗清楚証Taylor 的dy/dx已經係用左cos0=1,即sin90=0的定義。<br />\n<br />\n呢種解叫套套邏輯，用假設結論証明假設正確。<br />\n<br />\n樓上這位做的理解好好，值得欣賞。這條問題要答，就是因為「定義」！我地將三角函數引進廣義角時已講清楚：sin 角 = (unit circle的x坐標）咁自自然然sin90=1!<br />\n<br />\n勉強用番直角三角形解釋廣義角就不太恰當，因為自廣義角走出90度，正弦餘弦再不是邊比例，而是函數！[/quote]<br />\n其實Taylor Series果到只係想解番樓主話<br />\n「有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換<br />\n」"},{"pid":"6d20dc43050ba8edc7d64d1c32e278f9fbfc2f09","tid":331934,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"其實Taylor Series果到只係想解番樓主話<br />\n「有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換<br />\n」"},{"pid":"01ebb3382088bbc5b694db5514109db160b5e91c","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實Taylor Series果到只係想解番樓主話<br />\n「有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換<br />\n」</blockquote><br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐係sine係圓既軌跡<br />\n但運算sine wave時只有度數可以用taylor series計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc81896ab7eeb082123d7b3aec7b2dcdd3e31ed8","tid":331934,"uid":54270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實Taylor Series果到只係想解番樓主話<br />\n「有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換<br />\n」</blockquote><br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐係sine係圓既軌跡<br />\n但運算sine wave時只有度數可以用taylor series計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本就係come ftom taylor series<br />\n記得要轉rad至好計"},{"pid":"71971e98da32b1bc45d6bdf822916fd4a94dca19","tid":331934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實Taylor Series果到只係想解番樓主話<br />\n「有條function f(x)=2x+3<br />\n右邊2x+3係運算到<br />\n咁f(x)=sin x<br />\n個sin x係我地冇得就咁解架<br />\nSin x係咩公式轉換<br />\n」</blockquote><br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐係sine係圓既軌跡<br